getAgentCount().details: Get the total number of registered agents

returns.count: The total count of registered agents

params.agentAddress: The EVM address of the agent
params.agentDomain: The domain where the agent's AgentCard is hosted

returns.agentId: The unique identifier assigned to the agent

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

params.newAgentAddress: New address (zero address to keep current)
params.newAgentDomain: New domain (empty string to keep current)

newAgent(string,address).notice: Requires 0.005 ETH fee which is burned

updateAgent(uint256,string,address).notice: Only callable by the agent's current address or authorized delegate
